title: Celebrity Gossip- Lizzo Didn't Like Her Songs Ranked
description: Eminem’s daughter is opening up about how her dad’s past substance abuse affected her as a teenager. And Lizzo felt a little offended when she saw a list that ranked her songs from worst to best.
